[normal]increasingly
[normal],
[normal] TV and radio programmes, in particular dramas, feature unacceptable levels of violent, sexual and sexually violent material and bad language. 
[normal]We continue to experience biased reporting of news an
[normal]d current affairs, indeed reports of BBC bias are far too frequent
[normal], and not without foundation.
[normal]Should the BBC’s output and services be provided to any greater or lesser degree for particular audiences?[bold]Lord Hall said, “Now we deliver so much more with fou
